text: Stjarnan F.C. (Stjarnan Knattspyrnudeild; English: Star F.C.) is an Icelandic sports club from Garðabær. It was founded in 1960. It is best known for their association football team. The men's football team has won the Úrvalsdeild once. The women's team has won it three times. The volleyball team has also won the Icelandic Championship five times. == Other websites == * * Official football club website Category:1960 establishments in Europe Category:Sports clubs Category:Sport in Iceland Category:Icelandic football clubs Category:20th-century establishments in Iceland
